3公克，併同無法與之完全析離之包裝袋1個。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2875%2c20220928%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,2875,20220928,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2875","JDATE":"20220928","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}